      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model inputs documented with sources and uncertainty estimates; sensitivity of QoI to key inputs assessed.",
      "rationale": "Fluid density, viscosity, hemolysis model coefficients, and geometric dimensions documented with sources and nominal uncertainty ranges. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis performed for top-5 influential inputs. Hemolysis model coefficient C identified as highest-sensitivity parameter; uncertainty contribution bounded at ±11% of NIH prediction."
    },
