      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2. Qualitative review confirms validation operating conditions (2.5 L/min at 2500 RPM through 6.0 L/min at 3500 RPM) span the COU operating envelope. No extrapolation beyond validated range required for worst-case identification task."
